'''Xozhixi''' was the ancient [[Vratix/Legends|Vratix]] name for the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Thyferra/Legends|Thyferra]]. In the decade prior to the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]&mdash;the time known to the Vratix as [[Alazhixazha]]&mdash;the city regained its ancient name for the first time in a thousand [[Standard year/Legends|years]].

